  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.6.0-alpha02\" data-text=\"Version 1.6.0-alpha02\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.6.0-alpha02</h3>\n<p>April 15, 2021</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.core:core:1.6.0-alpha02</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.core:core-ktx:1.6.0-alpha02</code> are released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/5c42896eb6591b09e3952030fb7ea8d9b8c42713..079dd60d7d581a10fe71f976c3194c150ef1dd58/core\">Version 1.6.0-alpha02 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Add <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">TelephoneManagerCompat</code> and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">SubscriptionManagerCompat</code> (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I5568d5ef665d140ec998adbbf7681870a1c84ee2\">I5568d</a>)</li>\n<li>Remove deprecated <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">addCapabilityBinding</code> method from <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ShortcutInfoCompat</code> (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Ie8f70595bd410b6db5d4473f78d9423f4d7ea10c\">Ie8f70</a>)</li>\n<li>Add <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">addCapabilityBinding</code> with parameters and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">addCapabilityBinding</code> without parameters setters to <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ShortcutInfoCompat.Builder</code>, deprecated old <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">addCapabilityBinding</code> (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I906865532502b3bc2246bc79d32e64d7a2173c8f\">I90686</a>)</li>\n<li>Add <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">LocationCompat</code> class and\n<code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">LocationManagerCompat.getCurrentLocation()</code> (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I78d9ad233c3381477612bb9b382ca0cb60ce01a6\">I78d9a</a>)</li>\n<li>Deprecated <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ModeCompat.isNative</code> which is replaced by <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">DisplayCompat.getMode</code>. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I9a6a2cc601ac0fb41501ef5ac9e0aaa105a9d11d\">I9a6a2</a>)</li>\n<li>Added <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ContextCompat.getAttributionTag()</code> and\n<code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">UserHandleCompat.getUserHandleForUid()</code> (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/Iea4861c037732310318f97c359206a704573777a\">Iea486</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>External Contribution</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Backport tintable background and check mark for <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">CheckedTextView</code> (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I8575c5c23240a14153654ffafd0387fa89f2a3bc\">I8575c</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
  "commitsUrl": "https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/5c42896eb6591b09e3952030fb7ea8d9b8c42713..079dd60d7d581a10fe71f976c3194c150ef1dd58/core"
